Program: Omnibus
Title: Living Left-handed
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376kkz
Last Broadcast Date: 23 April 1993
Marilyn Monroe, Leonardo da Vinci, Albert Einstein were all left-handed. Words such as gauche, gawky and sinister all derive from words for left. An investigation into the superstitions around left-handedness, and a look at its links with creativeness.